				</ol>
			</nav>
			<h1>Polyaspartic Coating</h1>
			<p class="page-subtitle">
				Fast-curing, UV-stable systems that offer superior durability and can be installed in a single day for most projects
			</p>
		</section>
	</Container>

	<!-- Service Hero Section -->
	<Container>
		<section class="service-hero">
			<div class="hero-content">
				<div class="hero-text">
					<h2>Next-Generation Coating Technology</h2>
					<p>
						When time is critical and performance can't be compromised, polyaspartic coatings 
						deliver both. These advanced systems cure rapidly while maintaining superior 
						durability and UV stability. With military-precision application, we can transform 
						your space in a single day without sacrificing quality or longevity.
					</p>
					<div class="key-benefits">
						<div class="benefit-item">
							<span class="benefit-icon">‚ö°</span>
							<span>Same-Day Installation</span>
						</div>
						<div class="benefit-item">
							<span class="benefit-icon">‚òÄÔ∏è</span>
							<span>UV Stable - Won't Yellow</span>
						</div>
						<div class="benefit-item">
